---
// IA Section - L'IA chez Smice
---

<section class="ia-section" id="ia">
  <div class="ia-container">
    <h2 class="ia-title">
      L'<span class="highlight-yellow ia-blue ia-iaword"><span class="ia-ia-text">IA</span>
        <img src="/images/homepage/ia/subline-IA.png" alt="soulignement IA" class="ia-subline" />
      </span> chez Smice, évidemment.
    </h2>
    
    <div class="ia-content">
      <div class="ia-image-group">
        <img src="/images/homepage/ia/illustration.png" alt="L'IA chez Smice" class="ia-illustration" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="ia-text">
        <blockquote class="ia-quote">
          "Grâce à notre communauté, nous pouvons déployer vos programmes qualité rapidement et efficacement, quel que soit le secteur ou la localisation.
        </blockquote>
        <p class="ia-description">
          Nos profils sont soigneusement sélectionnés selon vos critères : expérience, type de mission, et zone géographique."
        </p>
        
        <div class="ia-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">
            <img src="/images/homepage/ia/ceo-avatar.png" alt="Julien Mondhard" />
          </div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <span class="author-name">Julien Mondhard</span>
            <span class="author-role">CEO - Smice</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ia-section {
    background-color: #E8EDF8;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .ia-container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ia-title {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #435888;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 50px 0;
  }

  .ia-title .ia-blue {
    color: #6989D4;
    font-weight: 800;
  }


  .ia-title .highlight-yellow {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ia-title .ia-iaword {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: bottom;
  }

  .ia-title .ia-subline {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 80%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 90px;
    height: auto;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
    display: block;
  }

  .ia-title .highlight-yellow::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 4px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 8px;
    background: #FFE566;
    border-radius: 4px;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .ia-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  /* Image Section */
  .ia-image-group {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ia-illustration {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  /* Text Section */
  .ia-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ia-quote {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #7C797F;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .ia-description {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #7C797F;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .ia-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: #D1D5DB;
  }

  .author-avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4A5FC1;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #6B7280;
  }

  /* ===== Tablet Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .ia-section {
      padding: 60px 24px;
    }

    .ia-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .ia-content {
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .ia-image-group {
      height: 400px;
    }

    .ia-bg-shape {
      width: 320px;
      height: 350px;
    }

    .ia-ceo-container {
      width: 240px;
      height: 350px;
    }

    .ia-bloc-verbatims,
    .ia-bloc-campagnes {
      width: 170px;
    }

    .ia-quote,
    .ia-description {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Mobile Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ia-section {
      padding: 50px 20px;
    }

    .ia-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 35px;
    }

    .ia-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 35px;
    }

    .ia-image-group {
      height: 380px;
    }

    .ia-bg-shape {
      width: 280px;
      height: 320px;
    }

    .ia-ceo-container {
      width: 220px;
      height: 320px;
    }

    .ia-bloc-verbatims {
      width: 150px;
      top: 10px;
      left: 10px;
    }

    .ia-bloc-campagnes {
      width: 150px;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 10px;
    }

    .ia-text {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ia-quote,
    .ia-description {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .ia-author {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Small Mobile ===== */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ia-title {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .ia-title .highlight-yellow::after {
      height: 6px;
      bottom: 2px;
    }

    .ia-image-group {
      height: 340px;
    }

    .ia-bg-shape {
      width: 240px;
      height: 280px;
    }

    .ia-ceo-container {
      width: 180px;
      height: 280px;
    }

    .ia-bloc-verbatims,
    .ia-bloc-campagnes {
      width: 130px;
      left: 0;
    }

    .author-avatar {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
    }

    .author-name {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>
